Package com.lonepulse.robozombie.response

Contains the set of core and auxiliary classes which process requests of successful request executions for a proxy invocation using the annotated meta-data found on the endpoint definition.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
Deserializer<OUTPUT> This contract defines the policy for a deserializer which reads the response content of a successful request execution and converts it to a desired entity type which can be processed in memory.
 

Class Summary
AbstractDeserializer<OUTPUT> An abstract implementation of Deserializer which directs deserialization for all Deserializers.
AsyncHandler<RESPONSE> To be used with asynchronous request execution for retrieving the deserialized response content or for gaining insight into any failures and errors which might have occurred.
PlainDeserializer This AbstractDeserializer extracts the response data as a raw String.
ResponseProcessorChain This is a concrete implementation of AbstractProcessorChain which creates a sequentially executed series of AbstractResponseProcessors responsible for handling the HttpResponse of an endpoint request invocation.
 

Enum Summary
Deserializers Exposes all available AbstractDeserializers, resolves concrete instances of their deserializer types and mediates communication.
 

Package com.lonepulse.robozombie.response Description
